hadiths[24]{hadithnumber,text}:
1524,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ma'siyat (nafarmaani) key kamon mein nazar jayez nahin hai, aur is ka kaffara wohi hai jo qism ka kaffara hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees sahih nahin hai, isliye ke Zohri ney is ko abu-Salma sey nahin suna hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko ye kehtey huye suna hai ke is hadees ko kaee logon ney riwayat kiya hai, inhi mein Musa bin Aqba aur ibne-Abi Ateeq hain, in dono ney Zohri sey ba-tareeq : (Suleman bin Arqam an Yahya bin abi Kasir an abi Salma an Aaysha an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai, Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : wo hadees yehi hai (aur aagey aa rahi hai). 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Jabir aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1525,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah ki nafarmaani par mabni (based) koi nazar jayez nahin hai, aur is ka kaffara wohi hai jo qism ka kaffara hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- aur abu-Safwaan ki is hadees sey jisey wo Yunus sey riwayat kartey hain, ziyada sahih hai. 3- abu-Safwaan Makki hain, inka naam Abdullah bin Saeed bin Abdul-Malik bin Marwan hai, in sey Humedi aur kaee badey badey muhaddeseen ney riwayat ki hai. 4- ehle-ilm Sahaba ki eik jamaat aur doosrey log kehtey hain : Allah ki ma'siyat (nafarmaani) key silsiley mein koi nazar nahin hai aur is ka kaffara wohi hai jo qism ka kaffara hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq ka yehi qol hai, in dono ney Zohri ki is hadees sey daleel kya hai jisey wo abu-Salma sey aur abu-Salma Aaisha sey riwayat kartey hain. 5- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey log kehtey hain : ma'siyat (nafarmani) mein koi nazar jayez nahin hai, aur is mein koi kaffara bhi nahin, Malik aur Shafai ka yehi qol hai."
1526,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs nazar maaney ke wo Allah ki itaat karega to wo Allah ki itaat karey , aur jo shakhs nazar maaney ke wo Allah ki nafarmani karega to wo Allah ki nafarmani na karey.'' is sanad sey bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Yahya bin Abi Kasir ney bhi Qasim bin Muhammad sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka yehi qol hai, Malik aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai, ye log kehtey hain ke Allah ki nafarmani na karey aur jab nazar Allah ki nafarmani ki baabat ho to is mein qism ka kaffara nahin hai."
1527,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''bande key ikhtiyar mein jo chiz nahin hai is mein nazar sahih nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain.
1528,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ghair mutayyan nazar ka kaffara wohi hai jo qism ka kaffara hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai.
1529,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Abdur-Rehman ! mansab amaarat (aohda ya pad) ka mutalba na karo, isliye ke agar tum ney isey mang kar hasil kiya to tum isi key supurd kar diye jaaogey, aur agar wo tumhen bin maangey mili to Allah ki madad aur tofiq tumharey shamil hogi , aur jab tum kisi kaam par qism khaao phir doosrey kaam ko us sey behtar samjho to jisey tum behtar samajhtey ho usey hi karo aur apni qism ka kaffara ada kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdur-Rehman bin Samura ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Jabir , Adi bin Hatim , Abu-Darda , Anas , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Amr , Abu-Hurera , Umme-Salma aur abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1530,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo aadmi kisi Amr (baat) par qism khaye , aur iskey ilawa kaam ko is sey behtar samjhey to wo apni qism ka kaffara ada karey aur wo kaam karey (jisey wo behtar samajhta hai).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- aksar ehle-ilm Sahaba aur deegar logon ka isi par amal hai ke qism todney sey pehley kaffara ada karna sahih hai, Malik bin Anas , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : « حانث » honey ( yani qism todney ( key baad hi kaffara ada kya jaeyga. 5- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : agar koi « حانث » honey ( yani qism todney ( key baad kaffara ada karey to merey nazdik ziyada achchha hai aur agar « حانث » honey sey pehley kaffara ada karey to bhi durust hai."
1531,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi Amr (baat) par qism khai aur sath hi Inshallah kaha, to is qism ko todney ka kaffara nahin hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is hadees ko Ubedullah bin Amr waghera ney Nafey sey, Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey moqufan riwayat kya hai, isi tarah is hadees ko Salim bin Aleh ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey moqufan riwayat ki hai, hamein nahin malum ke Ayub Sakhtiyaan key siwa kisi aur ney bhi isey marfooan riwayat kiya hai, Ismail bin Ibrahim kehtey hain : Ayub is ko kabhi marfooan riwayat kartey they aur kabhi marfooan nahin riwayat kartey they, 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- aksar ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai ke jab qism key sath (Insha-Allah) ka jumla mila ho to is qism ko todney ka kaffara nahin hai, Sufiyan Sory , Auzaai , Malik bin Anas , Abdullah bin Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq ka yehi qol hai."
1532,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney qism khai aur Insha-Allah kaha , wo « حانث » nahin huwa.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein sawal kiya to unhoney kaha : is hadees mein ghalati hai, is mein Abdur-Razzaaq sey ghalati hui hai, unhoney is ko Maamar ki hadees sey ikhtisaar kar diya hai, Maamar is ko basanad (ibne Taaus an Abeeh an abi Huraira an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kartey hain ke aap ney farmaya : ''Suleman bin Dawud (Aleh.) ney kaha : ( Allah ki qism ! ( aaj raat mein sattar biwiyon key paas zarur jaunga, har aurat sey eik ladka paida hoga, wo sattar biwiyon key paas gaey, un mein sey kisi aurat ney bachcha nahin jana, sirf eik aurat ney aadhey (naqis) bachchey ko janm diya.'' , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''agar unhon (Suleman (Alaihissalam)) ney (Insha-Allah) keh diya hota to wesay hi hota jaisa unhoney kaha tha.'' , isi tarah ye hadees puri tafsil key sath Abdur-Razzaaq sey aai hai, Abdur-Razzaaq ney basanad (Maamar an ibne Taaus an Abeeh) riwayat ki hai is mein (على سبعين امرأة) key bajaey (سبعين امرأة) hai, ye hadees Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey deegar sanadon sey aai hai, (is mein ye hai ke) wo Nabi Akaram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey (yun) riwayat kartey hain ke aap ney farmaya : ''Suleman bin Dawud ney kaha : aaj raat main sau biwiyon key paas zarur jaaunga.''"
1533,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna : merey baap ki qism ! merey baap ki qism ! aap ney (unhen bula kar) farmaya : ''suno ! Allah ney tumhen apney baap dada ki qism khaney sey mana farmaya hai.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Allah ki qism iskey baad mainey (baap dada ki) qism nahin khai, na jaan-bujh kar aur na hi kisi ki baat naqal kartey huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Sabit bin Zuhaak , ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , Qutaila aur Abdur-Rehman bin Samura (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- abu Ubaid kehtey hain ke umr key qol (ولا آثرا) key ye maana hain (لم آثره an غيري) (mainey doosrey ki taraf sey bhi naqal nahin kiya) Arab is jumle ko (لم أذكره an غيري) key maana mein istimal kartey hain."
1534,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik qafile mein paya , wo apney baap ki qism kha rahey they, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''beshak Allah tum logon ko baap , dada ki qism khaney sey mana farmata hai, qism khaney wala Allah ki qism khaye warna chup chaap rahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1535,"Ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney eik aadmi ko kehtey suna : aisa nahin qism hai Kaba ki, to us sey kaha : ghairullah ki qism na khai jaey, kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' jisney ghairullah ki qism khai usney kufr kiya ya shirk kiya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is hadees ki tafseer baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik ye hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka farman (فقد كفر أو أشرك) tanbih aur taghleez key taur par hai, iski daleel ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney umr ko kehtey suna : merey baap ki qism , merey baap ki qism ! to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' Allah baap , dada ki qism khaney sey mana farmata hai.''  neez (isi ke saath) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki) riwayat (ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Laat aur Uzzaa ki qism khai wo (لا إله إلا الله) kahey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 3- ye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key us farman ki tarah hai, beshak riya , shirk hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney aayate-karima :(فمن كان يرجو لقاء ربه فليعمل عملا صالحا) (Al Kahaf : 110)ki ye tafseer ki hai ke wo riya na karey."
1536,"Eik aurat ney nazar maana ke wo Baitullah tak (pedal) chal kar jaeygi, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is silsiley mein sawal kiya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''Allah taala uskey (pedal) chalney sey be-niyaz hai, usey hukm do ke wo sawar ho kar jaey.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Aqba bin Aamir aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log kehtey hain ke jab aurat (Hajj ko pedal) chal kar janey ki nazar maan ley to wo sawar ho jaey aur eik bakri dam mein dey."
1537,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik boodhey key qarib sey guzrey jo apney do beton key saharey (Hajj key liye) chal raha tha, aap ney puchha : kya maamla hai inka? logon ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! inhoney (pedal) chalney ki nazar maana hai, aap ney farmaya : '' Allah iskey apni jaan ko azab deney sey be-niyaz hai.''  phir aap ney us ko sawar honey ka hukm diya۔ is sanad sey bhi Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi jaisi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai. aur ye sahih hadees hai."
1538,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' nazar mat mano , isliye ke nazar taqdir key samney kuchh kaam nahin aati , sirf bakheel aur kanjus ka maal is tareeqe sey nikal liya jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey logon ka isi par amal hai, wo log nazar ko makrooh samajhtey hain. 4- Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain : nazar key andar karahat ka mafhoom itaa'at aur ma'siyat (nafarmani) dono sey mutalliq hai, agar kisi ney itaat ki nazar maana aur usey pura kiya to usey is nazar key pura karney ka ajr milega, lekin ye nazar makrooh hogi."
1539,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! mainey jahiliyat mein nazar maana thi ke eik raat Masjide-Haram mein aetikaf karunga, (to iska hukm bataeyn?) aap ney farmaya : ''apni nazar puri karo.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka maslak isi hadees key muwaafiq hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab koi Islam laye, aur uskey ooper jahiliyat ki nazar itaa'at wajib ho to usey puri karey. 4- baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba aur doosrey log kehtey hain ke baghair rozey key aetikaf nahin hai aur doosrey ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke aetikaaf par roza wajib nahin hai siwaye iske ke wo khud apney ooper (nazar mantey waqt) roza wajib kar ley, un logon ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki is hadees sey daleel kya hai ke unhoney jahiliyat main eik raat key aetikaf ki nazar maana thi, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney in ko nazar puri karney ka hukm diya (aur rozey ka koi zikr nahin kiya), Ahmed aur Is-haq ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1540,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam qism khatey they to aksar (لا ومقلب القلوب) kehtey they ''nahin, dilon key badalney waley ki qasam.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1541,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''jisney eik momin ghulam ko azad kiya, Allah is ghulam key har uzu key badley azad karney waley key eik eik uzu ko aag sey azad karega, yahan tak ke us (ghulam) ki sharmgaah key badley iski sharmgaah ko azad karega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih , gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , Amr bin Abasa ibne-Abbas , Waasila bin Isqaa', abu-Umama , Aqba bin Aamir aur Kaab bin Murra (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1542,"Soorate-haal ye thi ke hum saat bhai they, hamarey paas eik hi khaadima thi, hum mein sey kisi ney us ko tamaancha maar diya, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hukm diya ke hum us ko azad kar den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey Husain bin Abdur-Rehman sey kaee logon ney riwayat kiya hai, baaz logon ney apni riwayat mein ye zikr kiya hai ke Suwed bin Muqrin Muzni ney (لطمها على وجهها) kaha yani ''us ney uskey chehrey par tamaancha maara.'' 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1543,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney Islam key siwa kisi doosrey mazhab ki jhooti qism khai wo wesey hi ho gaya jaisey usney kaha.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka is masley mein ikhtilaf hai ke jab koi Islam key siwa kisi doosrey mazhab ki qism khaye aur ye kahey : agar usney aisa aisa kiya to Yahudi ya nasrani hoga, phir usney wo kaam kar liya , to baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke usney bahut bada gunah kiya lekin is par kaffara wajib nahin hai, ye ehale-Madina ka qol hai, Malik bin Anas bhi isi key qaail hain aur abu Ubaid ney bhi isi ko ikhtiyar kiya hai. 3- aur Sahaba aur Tabe-een waghera mein sey baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke is surat mein is par kaffara wajib hai, Sufiyan , Ahmed aur Is-haq ka yehi qol hai."
1544,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! meri behan ney nazar maana hai ke wo chadar odhey baghair nangey paaon chal kar Khana-Kaaba tak jaeygi, to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Allah taala tumhari behan ki sakht koshish par kuchh nahin karega ! usey chahiye ke wo sawar ho jaey, chadar odh ley aur teen din key rozey rakhey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, Ahmed aur Is-haq ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1545,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum mein sey jisney qism khai aur apni qism mein kaha : Laat aur Uzzaa ki qism hai ! wo (لا إله إلا الله) kahey'' aur jis shakhs ney kaha : ''aao jua khelein wo sadqa karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1546,"Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik nazar key barey jo un ki maa par wajib thi aur usey puri karney sey pehley wo mar gaeen , fatwa puchha , to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''unki taraf sey nazar tum puri karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1547,"Aap ney farmaya : ''jo musalman kisi musalman ko azad karega , to ye azad karna uskey liye jahannam sey najat ka baais hoga, us azad kiye gaey mard ka har uzu us azad karney waley key uzu ki taraf sey kifaayat kerega, jo musalman do musalman aurton ko azad kerega, to ye dono uskey liye jahannam sey khulaasi ka baais hongi, un dono azad aurton ka har uzu uskey uzu ki taraf sey kifaayat karega , jo musalman aurat kisi musalman aurat ko azad kereygi , to ye uskey liye jahannam sey najat ka baais hogi, us azad ki gaee aurat ka har uzu us azad karney waley key uzu ki taraf sey kifaayat kerega.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- ye hadees daleel hai ke mardon key liye mard azad karna aurat key azad karney sey afzal hai, isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney kisi musalman mard ko azad kiya wo uskey liye jahannam sey najat ka baais hoga, us azad kiye gaey mard ka har uzu uskey uzu ki taraf sey kifaayat kerega.'' Raavi ney puri hadees bayan ki jo apni sanadon key aetbar sey sahih hai."
